$interpreted: Sophie: Where on earth did Elio go...?
Ru-yi: It's too crowded, I'm leaking!!!
Ru-yi: Why are there so many people on the streets today? *sigh*...I'm just a poor, tired whale.
Sophie: What are you doing here? Didn't Hanbei say that since Elio left on his own, he wouldn't help?
Hanbei: Who said I came to look for that good-for-nothing. Today's my day off. I'm just going for a stroll.
Ru-yi: When you were leaving you clearly said, "If we don't find him, that bonehead Sophie is going to worry herself to death."
Hutchinson: Secretly thinking of others but unwilling to admit it; this is Hanbei's way of being a gentleman.
Hanbei: Non...Nonsense!
Sophie: I know you all are worried about me. Thanks so much!!
Hanbei: This old and you still need a hug...cut it out already...
Rich Snob: Please stop!!
Dirty Old Man: Hey, sweet cakes. Won't you come and have a cup of tea with us?
Rich Snob: That's nice of you, but no thank you.
Skirt-Chaser: All woman are like this. Their mouth says no, but their body says yes.
Rich Snob: Let...let me go!!
Rune: Sophie, can I beat this guy?
Sophie: Of course. Perverts are the enemy of all!
Dirty Old Man: Please, no more. I'm begging you to let me go.
Sophie: Men are all like this. Your mouth says no, but you really want it.
Sophie: Rune, keep going.
Dirty Old Man: I'm sorry! Sorry! I was wrong!
Rich Snob: Soph!?
Rich Snob: I finally found you!
Rune: Let Sophie...go.
Hutchinson: Are you...Miss Minnie!?
Hanbei: So you just decide to show up out of nowhere?
Ru-yi: Huh? How do you all know her?
Hutchinson: Ah, yes. When Miss Minne left, Ru-yi had not yet joined the troupe, so they wouldn't have met.
Hutchinson: She's...Sophie mother.
Ru-yi: Sophie's mother!?
Sophie: No, she isn't!
Sophie: This woman...she...she abandoned me and my father 12 years ago and never showed any interest in me.
Sophie: So she's not my mother!
Minnie: Soph, let your mother explain...
Sophie: ......
Sophie: Okay everybody, we've already checked this whole area. We ought to go somewhere else to look for Elio.
Minnie: Soph...wait. Are you just going to ignore me?
Minnie: *groan*...
Hutchinson: Miss Minnie!? What's wrong?
Ru-yi: Sophie! She doesn't look too well!
